<lb n="2" break="no"/>vimalajalaparikṣālanē kṣīṇapāpā lōkāyasyōjvalaśrīkharanakha<supplied reason="omitted">ra</supplied>mu<unclear>khō</unclear>ddāritōsauhiraṇyaḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> tasmai jiyyakṣamābhṛt śikharivasatayē śrīnṛsiṁhāya bhaktaśśākābdē vyōmalōkāṁbarāśaśigaṇitamajjana <gap reason="lost" quantity="3" unit="character"/> tārtthaḥ [<g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> 9*] Ēkōttaranavatimitānkalaśā(ṁ)ntāmrēṇa nirmmitān prā
